{"tid":227803,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 台中三日兩夜遊","createTime":"2017-05-03T12:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T12:43:50.000Z","uid":99773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c24e352cc6864732254e69ac248ca9b76a0a51d1","tid":227803,"uid":99773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:37:12.000Z","msg":"交代返少少背景先，打算自己下星期去！<br />\n第一次想走得咁快，最近太多唔好嘅事發生，<br />\n去散散心平靜下心情，比自己放鬆下...<br />\n睇下有咩要注意嘅地方，希望各路人賜教！<br />\n<br />\n機票方面，已經留意緊係價位，<br />\n到而家都未book...要過埋聽日先搞得！<br />\n不過下星期就飛都預左唔會平...<br />\n但好似同自由行套票差無幾，所以仲諗緊<br />\n<br />\n住宿方面，諗住住青年旅舍，求推介！<br />\n揹一個書包去就算...唔會帶太多野！<br />\n上年去台灣，有個朋友都係無book，即日checkin...<br />\n<br />\n台證方面，好似轉左新制，<br />\n利伸都係上網ko...<br />\n<br />\n景點方面，完全無去過台中，<br />\n都係上網google下咁，睇下人地啲遊記，<br />\n跟下人地嘅足跡！"},{"pid":"56e271198c87da1374e06c0243bdbd0f797f03a2","tid":227803,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:38:42.000Z","msg":"如果冇台幣點算?去機場唱小小先啦"},{"pid":"9ca25a17726b4ad3b60a5d43541eb0eb75b12039","tid":227803,"uid":88777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:38:56.000Z","msg":"獨遊正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4405443c7de2f0f9d9adcc7959ff0c741b290e9","tid":227803,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:39:10.000Z","msg":"台灣機場不是香港機場"},{"pid":"36cf57cd5e558c63e4297f5b788dc797ca0c5d01","tid":227803,"uid":99773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:43:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果冇台幣點算?去機場唱小小先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗住去atm㩒"},{"pid":"544f47d44be68492aedfbbfe6898b56425dda99a","tid":227803,"uid":99773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>獨遊正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會好驚"},{"pid":"2868802d7d52aa62a6a3d4e0f99db561d1eed815","tid":227803,"uid":99773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,